; Nested Survex driver used by [Scanner][Survex] and [Attach][Cave]
; tests. Pulls in entrance.svx which in turn pulls in passage.svx,
; so the dependency closure has three files. The bareword + no-
; extension *include rule is exercised by its own self-contained
; test (avoids re-visit warnings tangling this fixture's contract).
*begin Nested
*include "entrance.svx"
*end Nested
